  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nAdmin Notifications that are marked `read` by performing any action (Accept/Decline) are marked as `unread` after the AC is closed and reopened.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nThe Admin notifications should be marked as read if the user performs any action (Accept / Decline) on the notification\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nThe Admin Notifications are marked as unread if we close the Activity Centre and reopen it again.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Received an Admin notification on Activity Center\r\n2) Accept / Decline the notification\r\n3) Notification will be marked as read until you close the Activity Center\r\n4) Close and reopen the Activity Center\r\n5) The admin notification which was Accepted/Declined would be marked unread.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status Version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
